## Version 1.2.0 (02/01/2023)

### New Features

- **AI-Powered Assistant:** We've integrated an advanced AI-powered assistant that can answer your questions, assist with tasks, and provide helpful suggestions. Say hello to the future of productivity!

- **Dark Mode:** Introducing a sleek and stylish dark mode option for our app. Now, you can work late into the night without straining your eyes.

- **Enhanced Security:** We've bolstered our security measures with multi-factor authentication (MFA) and end-to-end encryption. Your data is now safer than ever.

- **Collaborative Workspaces:** Create and collaborate with colleagues in real-time using our new collaborative workspaces. Say goodbye to endless email chains and hello to efficient teamwork.

- **Intuitive UI:** Our user interface has undergone a complete overhaul for a more user-friendly experience. Enjoy a more intuitive and visually pleasing interface.

- **Performance Boost:** We've optimized our app to be faster and more responsive, even on older devices. Experience blazing-fast performance across the board.

### Bug Fixes

- Fixed a critical bug that caused the app to crash when handling large data sets.

- Resolved an issue where some users were experiencing login problems on certain devices.

- Addressed a minor UI glitch that caused buttons to be misaligned on smaller screens.

### Enhancements

- Improved search functionality for faster and more accurate results.

- Streamlined onboarding process for new users, making it easier to get started.

- Enhanced error handling and reporting for a more seamless user experience.
